  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Be The Next Top Achiever",
  "description": "<p>Are you tired of your <strong>desk-bound job</strong>?<br />Do you want to meet different people and have different experience everyday?<br />Your <strong>effort</strong> and <strong>hard work</strong> are not reflected in your <strong>payslip</strong>?<br /></p><p><u><em><strong>If this is you then this might be your next big decision</strong></em></u><br /></p><p>Here at Innovation Organization, we are an outsourced marketing company, backed by our parent company, SalesWorks Singapore, that believe in building strong relationships with our clients is key to providing exceptional service. We take the time to understand our clients' needs and become experts in their business and brand, enabling us to provide tailored marketing solutions that meet their goals.<br /></p><p><u><strong>Who we want</strong></u></p><ul><li>Understands this is not a 'Get Rich Fast Place'</li><li>Willing to put in the effort and hard work to achieve what they want</li><li>Can work individually as well as in a team setting</li></ul><p><br />Face to face is what we do best. If you are interested to understand more on what we do and what opportunities we can provide, drop us a WhatsApp at <strong>88083166</strong> and we will arrange an interview session for you.</p>",
